root: ^I felt like I have slept for decades, burying myself under inches of snow.
^Just waking up drains all of my energy.
^I rest for a while, waiting for my senses to awake.
^I frowned, struggled to open my eyes and stumbled out of the freezer.
^All the peopel around me are dead.
^The air is stinky and a deadly silent drain me to another hell.
